# Furiosa LLM Models

Furiosa LLM Models (furiosa-llm-models) provides a few optimized LLM Models for Furiosa RNGD

## Formatting

Our CI checks Python source codes via [Ruff](https://docs.astral.sh/ruff/) which is a
Python linter also a code formatter.

### Installation

```shell
pip install ruff
```

### Format & Lint check

```shell
make lint
```

### Perform Formatting & Linting

```shell
make do-lint
```

